      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ANNIHILATE (3) was scintillating late when scorching home from the rear to only miss by a head here two weeks ago. Peaking now and is drawn to take much closer order. Will take plenty of stopping. CHILLCUZ (10) is proving a tough one to catch but has the late splits to keep supporters interested. Gets in at the minimum and will take fending off if the gaps appear. SCANDALIZE (2) has returned in great order and will only be further improved third-up. Already boasts a win at this trip, so the rise doesn't bother. Holder piloting from the inside also reads favourably. STOKOMO (1) sets up well off two strong runs to open the prep. Is another that should be hitting his straps and is sure to be competitive. ROYAL SCRIPTURE (6) and SEE YA LATER BABY (8) are the likely leaders and without other much pressure they can dictate. One of them can steal it, if they are too cute behind.",
